overview: Natalie is currently working on www.ifyouwanna.com, a marketplace for cleaners in London, UK. Natalie was educated in Australia and attended The University of Melbourne, where she obtained two degrees; a Bachelor of Science and a Bachelor of Commerce. Natalie started her professional career working in financial markets, establishing herself as an equities dealer at one of Australia’s largest investment houses. On moving to the UK she has immersed herself in the London start-up scene, basing herself at TechHub at Google Campus. Her aim as an entrepreneur is to revolutionise the way Londoners book cleaners for their homes.
